ita23" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chima Machida</a>将于12月13日星期三发行她的第一张迷你专辑“The Pages”。</p><p>为了纪念专辑的发行，Chima Machida 将被任命为 HMV&amp;BOOKS SHIBUYA 店的经理，为期一天，并于 12 月 13 日（周三）举行两次合影会，包括赠送活动限定名片。</p><p>同时，还将举办在HMV各店铺购物满2,500日元（含税）以上的顾客按照先到先得方式获得“町田Chima×HMV Fair限定优惠券卡”的活动。<a href="https://www.hmv.co.jp/news/article/231108125/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>了解展会详情。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000743.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>4位“VEE”人才迎新商品现已发售</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp 650w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-150x150.webp 150w" width="650" height="650" /></a></p><p>索尼音乐娱乐公司的虚拟艺人开发和管理项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/_vee_official_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VEE</a> ”已开始为其虚拟艺人<a href="https://twitter.com/ukiuki_unico" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yuiko Uki</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/HasumiSahiro" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sahiro Hasumi</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/hisumi_rihito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hibumi</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/MememoriAn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Morian Meme</a>销售欢迎商品。</p><p>备有“欢迎锡徽章”、“欢迎亚克力立牌”、“欢迎迷你横幅”。</p><p><a href="https://shop.vee-official.jp/s/ve01/?ima=5455" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>了解销售地点。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000079.000049041.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">索尼音乐娱乐公司