idth="500" height="375" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Nuy3XE8vjgc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCzUftO8KOVkV4wQG1vkUvg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hoshou Marine</strong></a>正在庆祝成立四周年。昔日非常火爆的昭和歌谣节又回来了，而且还升级了。 4:3比例的画面，类似阴极射线管的画面模糊，怀旧的字体，手绘的字幕，与合作伙伴完美协同的昭和音乐选择，复古可爱的偶像编舞，再现昭和时代，威力巨大。每个角落都充满了笑话，包括开头的复古动画以及与<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@GawrGura" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Gauru和Gura</strong></a>合作期间出现的超级骑师风格的90年代动画。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gccilsj09fya-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gccilsj09fya-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 966px) 100vw, 966px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gccilsj09fya-jpg.webp 966w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gccilsj09fya-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gccilsj09fya-768x576.webp 768w" width="966" height="725" /></a></p><p>和上次一样，大神澪和白神吹雪的MC表演也是亮点之一。白神吹雪仔细研究了昭和时代男播音员的说话方式，脱离音乐，滔滔不绝地讲有趣的故事，我认为这对于理解它的人来说非常有用。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[原创动漫MV]SHINKIRO[hololive/Hosho Marine/Gawr Gura]" width="500" height="375" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9ehwhQJ50gs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Hoshou Marine和Gauru Gura同时发行的新歌是一首全动画MV，融合了Gauru Gura最喜欢的日本城市流行音乐的味道。其特点是旋律悲伤，两人关系的故事有些感人。另外，这部动画中似乎有一些部分是由凤翔海洋负责剪辑的。</p><h2> 【生日企划】第一次！ #hololive体力王决胜赛！ ！ [雪花拉米/Hololive] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【生日企划】第一次！ #hololive体力王决胜赛！ ！ [雪花拉米/Hololive]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zj2euAGNarM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YukihanaLamy" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>雪花拉米</strong></a>举办了“第一届！#Hololive体能王大赛！！”作为生日项目。我与我的 Neporabo 成员一起支持并挑战挑战者。参加者是伊吕波一马，<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@kazamairoha" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>看上去</strong></a>玩得很开心，负责充满活力和兴奋<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@NatsuiroMatsuri" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>的夏日色彩祭，</strong></a>负责性感？<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@HoshimachiSuisei" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>井月</strong></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YuzukiChoco" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>巧克力</strong></a>、以乐观言论取笑的星町水<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ShiroganeNoel" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>成、语气悠闲、肌肉发达的白银诺埃尔</strong></a>、令人期待的超人<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@AmaneKanata" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>力量</strong></a>的天音彼方、动作自由自在的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@MomosuzuNene" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>桃铃宁宁</strong></a>。每一位选手都将挑战雪花拉米纸牌的结果。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.71z9qjqy7vuj-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.71z9qjqy7vuj-1024x582.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.71z9qjqy7vuj-1024x582.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.71z9qjqy7vuj-300x171.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.71z9qjqy7vuj-768x437.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83